  "sourceOfTruthCutover": {
    "canonicalNextSlice": "PrehistoricRush Runner Source Snapshot + Contact Smoke Authority Lock",
    "problem": "game-scenes.json, scenes/game.json, runner-tuning.json, kit-composition.json, kit-cutover-inventory.json, and flock-generation.json define product intent, but src/runtime-terrain-v6.mjs still duplicates live tuning, scene transitions, input semantics, contact outcomes, spawn budgets, win threshold, and snapshot authority inline.",
